  "detailed_description": "<strong>Task:</strong><br>Every day, you start at the top of your assigned underground station. Your job is to descend using the elevator, inspect and approve all <u>10</u> special items, and then return to the top.<br><br><strong>Warning:</strong><br>An increase in anomalous behavior has been reported. Detected anomalies must be removed; otherwise, <u>termination</u> procedures will be initiated.<br><br><strong>Contract Length:</strong><br>The contract lasts for 7 days, after which you will be released from <u>your</u> station.<br><br><strong><i><u>Good Luck</u></i></strong>",
